    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "so if the \"leading voices\" think the old way is insufficient, does that mean the \"tough on crime\" approach is basically just fundamentally flawed? like, is it even a valid way to manage a city if it doesn't actually address the root causes you mentioned?",
